ActOther Than Statutory Authority
PrecisAppointment of SÉBASTIEN CARRIÈRE as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Haiti; CHRISTOPHER COOTER as High Commissioner for Canada in the Kingdom of Lesotho, with residence in Pretoria; ELISSA GOLBERG as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Italian Republic and as Permanent Representative of Canada to the Food and Agriculture Organization, the World Food Programme and the International Fund for Agricultural Development, with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of San Marino, with residence in Rome; DEIRDRE KENT as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Kingdom of Norway; MARIANICK TREMBLAY as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Colombia; and ELIZABETH WILLIAMS as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Costa Rica, with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Honduras, with residence in San José.
